類比積體電路設計 - Analog Integrated Circuits Design




授課教師：  劉深淵
課程時間：105下－二789
上課地點：
										電二145；
修課資訊：
										【半年】【選修】【2,3,4 年級選修課程】【3學分】										
										
										
                                        

課程概述：

										本課程係以電機系，大三及大四學生為對象，每週三堂課，為選修課程，三學分的課程。本課程最主要是訓練學生運用電路模擬器(如hspice)來設計分析基本類比積體電路。為了加強學生的學習效果，本課程有作業練習、期中考試，和期末專題。使用教材以課本為主，相關書籍與資料為輔，共分為十五章。內容包括:chapter 1: introduction to analog design chapter 2: cmos processing technologychapter 3: layout and packagingchapter 4: basic mos device physicschapter 5: single-stage amplifierschapter 6: differential amplifierschapter 7: current mirrors and biasing techniqueschapter 8: frequency response of amplifierschapter 9: operational amplifierschapter 10: stability and frequency compensationchapter 11: nanometer design studieschapter 12: noisechapter 13: nonlinearity and mismatchchapter 14: bandgap referenceschapter 15: oscillatorschapter 16: phase-locked loop										

授課資訊：
										
										課程說明										

										;  臺大課程網										


註意事項：
										總人數限 50人                                    










雷射及非線性晶體應用 - Applications of Laser and Nonlinear Crystals




授課教師：  彭隆瀚
課程時間：105下－四789
上課地點：
										電二454；
修課資訊：
										【半年】【選修】【碩士班博士班 1,2 年級】【3學分】										
										
										
                                        

課程概述：

										wave propagation in anisotropic, jones matrix formulation, classical anharmonic oscillator model of nonlinear susceptibility, contraction and crystal symmetry, wave equation description of nonlinear optical interactions, phase matching & quasi-phase-matching, second harmonic generation, optical parametric amplification and oscillation, gaussian beam and geometric optics, abcd matrix and resonator designproperties of light in matterswave propagation in anisotropic (uniaxial, biaxial) crystals), jones matrix formulation of polarized light and optical components,nonlinear wave interactions between light and matterclassical anharmonic oscillator model of nonlinear susceptibility & nonlinear phenomena, contraction and crystal symmetry, wave equation description of nonlinear optical interactions, phase matching in uniaxial & biaxial crystalsnonlinear optics process for laser generation quasi-phase-matching, second harmonic generation, optical parametric amplification and oscillation,design of solid state lasersgaussian beam and geometric optics, abcd matrix and eigen modes of laser resonators										

授課資訊：
										
										課程說明										

										;  臺大課程網										


註意事項：
										總人數限18人。總人數限 18人                                    










